longBusinessSummary: International Dispensing Corporation designs, manufactures, and sells packaging and dispensing solutions. The company's products include The Answer, a low-acid and aseptic tap that can dispense liquid foods and beverages continuously without refrigeration. International Dispensing Corporation has strategic alliance with ALPLA Group. International Dispensing Corporation was incorporated in 1995 and is based in New York, New York.
